<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-wvfXpqpZZVQGK6TAh5PVlGOfQNHSoD2xbE+QkPxCAFlNEevoEH3Sl0sibVcOQVnN" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/3.5.2/animate.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="public/css/style.css">
<style>

*{
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

body{
  background:black;
  color:#485e74;
  line-height:1.6;
  font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
  padding:1em;
}

.container{
  max-width:1000px;
  margin-top: 50px;
  margin-bottom: 50px;
  padding:1em;
}

ul{
  list-style: none;
  padding:0;
}

.brand{
  text-align: center;
}

.brand span{
  color:#fff;
}

.wrapper{
  box-shadow: 0 0 20px 0 rgba(72,94,116,0.7);
}

.wrapper > *{
  padding: 1em;
}

.company-info{
  background:#c9e6ff;
}

.company-info h3, .company-info ul{
  text-align: center;
  margin:0 0 1rem 0;
}

.contact{
  background:#f9feff;
}

/* FORM STYLES */
.contact form{
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  grid-gap:20px;
}

.contact form label{
  display:block;
}

.contact form p{
  margin:0;
}

.contact form .full{
  grid-column: 1 / 3;
}

.contact form button, .contact form input, .contact form textarea{
  width:100%;
  padding:1em;
  border:1px solid #c9e6ff;
}

.contact form button{
  background:#c9e6ff;
  border:0;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.contact form button:hover,.contact form button:focus{
  background:#e1edfa;
  color:#fff;
  outline:0;
  transition: background-color 2s ease-out;
}

/* LARGE SCREENS */
@media(min-width:700px){
  .wrapper{
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
  }

  .wrapper > *{
    padding:2em;
  }

  .company-info h3, .company-info ul, .brand{
    text-align: left;
  }
</style>  


</head>

<body style="background-color: black;">
  <div class="menu-wrapper">
    <header class="header">
      <a href="/" class="logo"><img alt="Logo" src="/img/logo.jpg"><i class="fa fa-home" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
      <input class="menu-btn" type="checkbox" id="menu-btn" />
      <label class="menu-icon" for="menu-btn"><span class="navicon"></span></label>
      <ul class="menu">
        <li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li> 
        <li><a href="/contact">Contact Us</a></li> 
      </ul>
    </header>
  </div>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="wrapper animated bounceInLeft">
      <div class="company-info">
        <h3>Smart Water Solutions</h3>`
      </div>
        <form method="POST" action="about">
          <p>
            Smart Water Solutions is a wastewater management company that is registered and licensed. Our company is determined to obey all rules and regulations guiding the wastewater management industry, hire well trained and competent to handle water pipelines and install necessary equipment to detect water leakages in Johannesburg.
We are in business to provide modern and smart, 4IR driven solutions to the water problems Johannesburg is facing. We are specifically focusing on Johannesburg because we saw that the amount of water that is lost in a month is very large as a result of that, water is becoming scarce and limited to various households around Johannesburg. 
We as a company are more than prepared to go an extra mile to ensure that water wastage is at its minimal in Johannesburg. Our customers and potential customers can rest assured that they will get quality services at competitive rates.
In our company our goal is to provide a smart water solution that will assist in mitigation of water leakages around Johannesburg. We intend to mitigate water leakages by developing a 4IR enabled web application, which is going to be the first of its kind in South Africa. With this technology we believe that we can be successful in mitigating water leakages and also help improve service delivery in Johannesburg

          </p>
          
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>